    "content": "<h2>10 Dating Profile Photo Mistakes</h2><p>1. Outdated photos (5+ years old). 2. Sunglasses in main photo — eyes are the most important feature. 3. Group photo as main photo. 4. Bathroom/mirror selfies. 5. No smiling — smiling gets 14% more matches. 6. Over-filtered photos. 7. Photos with exes. 8. Only one photo — 3+ photos get 5x more engagement. 9. Blurry or low-resolution photos. 10. Photos that misrepresent your current appearance.</p>",
