    "content": "<h2>Dating After 50 in 2026</h2><p>The 50+ dating market has grown significantly — 28% of adults over 50 are single and actively dating. Best apps: eHarmony (compatibility-focused, strong 50+ user base), Match.com (large diverse pool, excellent search filters), OurTime (dedicated 50+ platform), SilverSingles (personality-based matching for 50+). Profile tips for 50+: use recent photos, be honest about your life situation (children, grandchildren, retirement plans), lead with your genuine personality rather than trying to appear younger. Safety: seniors remain disproportionately targeted by romance scammers — never send money to someone you haven't met. The mindset advantage: by 50, most people know exactly what they want and what they don't — use this clarity as an asset.</p>",
